7397:../Core/FreeRTOS-Kernel/tasks.c ****         /*
7398:../Core/FreeRTOS-Kernel/tasks.c ****          * PLEASE NOTE:
7399:../Core/FreeRTOS-Kernel/tasks.c ****          *
7400:../Core/FreeRTOS-Kernel/tasks.c ****          * This function is provided for convenience only, and is used by many
7401:../Core/FreeRTOS-Kernel/tasks.c ****          * of the demo applications.  Do not consider it to be part of the
7402:../Core/FreeRTOS-Kernel/tasks.c ****          * scheduler.
7403:../Core/FreeRTOS-Kernel/tasks.c ****          *
7404:../Core/FreeRTOS-Kernel/tasks.c ****          * vTaskGetRunTimeStatistics() calls uxTaskGetSystemState(), then formats part
7405:../Core/FreeRTOS-Kernel/tasks.c ****          * of the uxTaskGetSystemState() output into a human readable table that
7406:../Core/FreeRTOS-Kernel/tasks.c ****          * displays the amount of time each task has spent in the Running state
7407:../Core/FreeRTOS-Kernel/tasks.c ****          * in both absolute and percentage terms.
7408:../Core/FreeRTOS-Kernel/tasks.c ****          *
7409:../Core/FreeRTOS-Kernel/tasks.c ****          * vTaskGetRunTimeStatistics() has a dependency on the snprintf() C library
7410:../Core/FreeRTOS-Kernel/tasks.c ****          * function that might bloat the code size, use a lot of stack, and
7411:../Core/FreeRTOS-Kernel/tasks.c ****          * provide different results on different platforms.  An alternative,
7412:../Core/FreeRTOS-Kernel/tasks.c ****          * tiny, third party, and limited functionality implementation of
7413:../Core/FreeRTOS-Kernel/tasks.c ****          * snprintf() is provided in many of the FreeRTOS/Demo sub-directories in
7414:../Core/FreeRTOS-Kernel/tasks.c ****          * a file called printf-stdarg.c (note printf-stdarg.c does not provide
7415:../Core/FreeRTOS-Kernel/tasks.c ****          * a full snprintf() implementation!).
7416:../Core/FreeRTOS-Kernel/tasks.c ****          *
7417:../Core/FreeRTOS-Kernel/tasks.c ****          * It is recommended that production systems call uxTaskGetSystemState()
7418:../Core/FreeRTOS-Kernel/tasks.c ****          * directly to get access to raw stats data, rather than indirectly
7419:../Core/FreeRTOS-Kernel/tasks.c ****          * through a call to vTaskGetRunTimeStatistics().
7420:../Core/FreeRTOS-Kernel/tasks.c ****          */
7421:../Core/FreeRTOS-Kernel/tasks.c **** 
